CREATE TABLE users (
  id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
  timestamp REAL DEFAULT 0.1,
  username TEXT NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  email TEXT NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  photo BLOB,
  admin INTEGER NOT NULL,
  birth_date TEXT,
  last_login TEXT,
  automatic_logout TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE users (
  id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY IDENTITY,
  timestamp FLOAT DEFAULT 0.1,
  username VARCHAR(MAX) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  email VARCHAR(MAX) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  photo VARBINARY,
  admin BIT NOT NULL,
  birth_date DATE,
  last_login DATETIME,
  automatic_logout TIME
)
